1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 5=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:17,460 --> 00:01:20,380
(Zhou Manor)

18
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,840
Thanks.

19
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,120
What about mine?

20
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,400
Huh?

21
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,840
That's more like it.

22
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,080
I know

23
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,000
the sight of me makes your blood boil.

24
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,800
But don't worry.

25
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,040
Once I've earned enough money,

26
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,960
I'll take Yu away from here

27
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,400
to make a fresh start.

28
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,400
When have I ever been angry
at the sight of you?

29
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,400
You two aren't going anywhere.

30
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,800
(Ms. Zhou,)

31
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,600
(are you out of your mind, or am I?)

32
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,200
(You want me to stay)

33
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,160
(as you watch me flirt with Yu)

34
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,240
(right under your nose day after day?)

35
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,280
(What kind of bizarre hobby is that?)

36
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,400
Don't worry.

37
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,200
Even if I leave the Zhou Manor,

38
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,040
I'll still lend a hand

39
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,320
with your Gambiered Silk business.

40
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,800
Well, didn't see that coming.

41
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,680
Yes,

42
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,640
I did misunderstand you before.

43
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,160
But I never expected

44
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,840
you'd be this capable.

45
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,000
Not only did you outmatch Lu Qifeng

46
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,120
in verses,

47
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,120
but you also helped restore and improve

48
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,400
the Gambiered Silk technique,

49
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,000
pulling the Zhous
out of an urgent crisis.

50
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,440
Now

51
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:39,040
the misunderstanding is cleared up.

52
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,800
Seems like it's not cleared up yet.

53
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:45,400
About matters of the heart, you know.

54
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,200
You get it, right?

55
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,000
Why are you staring at me?

56
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,600
I don't get any

57
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,480
matters of the heart.

58
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:54,880
(That's exactly why I'm scared.
You don't understand.)

59
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,800
Anyway,

60
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,800
I'll work hard to earn money.

61
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,200
Alright.

62
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,840
And then

63
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,200
keep helping sell the Gambiered Silk.

64
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,200
Alright.

65
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:11,320
And then I'll have to find someone

66
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,680
I actually like

67
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,880
to marry and have kids, right?

68
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,400
Hmm?

69
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,040
Ugh, I can't talk about this anymore.

70
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,720
I'm sleepy.

71
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,400
I'm going to bed.

72
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,400
I just realized

73
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,360
that Li Yunhe

74
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,080
isn't entirely worthless.

75
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,200
He actually has some good points.

76
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,280
See? I told you.

77
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,800
You can't judge a person
by first impressions.

78
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,040
You used to

79
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,480
be far too impatient.

80
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,240
How was I supposed to know

81
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,880
he had so many tricks up his sleeve?

82
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,720
Wait a minute.

83
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,600
Don't tell me

84
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,520
you've taken a liking to him, too.

85
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,600
Xingyu,

86
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,600
why don't you divorce him?

87
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,640
I'll take him as my live-in husband.

88
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,000
That way, the Marquis House

89
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,680
won't trouble the Zhou family anymore.

90
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,520
And you can
marry into the Marquis House,

91
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,840
enjoying a life of wealth and honor.

92
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,720
Wealth and honor?

93
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,600
If you like it so much,
you marry Lu Qifeng.

94
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,400
I wish I could,

95
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,720
but Lu Qifeng

96
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,720
doesn't fancy me at all.

97
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,440
I must be coming down with a cold.

98
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,000
I'm warning you,

99
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,800
if you keep this up,

100
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,800
we can't be family anymore.

101
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,760
Oh, come on, Xingyu.

102
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,760
Here's an idea.

103
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,600
Take me with you when you go out.

104
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,080
I want to be around Li Yunhe, too.

105
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,120
I want

106
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,320
to admire his talent up close.

107
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:46,880
Hmm.

108
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,120
Don't worry,

109
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:50,680
I'll be very low-key.

110
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,920
What are you talking about?

111
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:53,840
Did you forget?

112
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,440
Right now, you're the Zhou heiress.

113
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,600
Oh, right.

114
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,000
Yes, I am.

115
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,400
I'm the Zhou heiress right now.

116
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,720
But

117
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,320
when are you going to

118
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,000
come clean to him about your identity?

119
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,240
I'll keep it hidden as long as I can.

120
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,840
Li Yunhe,

121
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,960
just wait till you get a taste
of what I can do.

122
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:23,260
(Zhou Manor)

123
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,920
Mr. Li, my lady requests your presence.

124
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,640
Ms. Zhou?

125
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,800
In the dead of night,

126
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,440
what does she want with me?

127
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,520
She didn't say.

128
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:44,240
Fine, got it.

129
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,440
Ms. Zhou!

130
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,960
It's already quite late,

131
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,240
and we're alone here.

132
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,560
What do you want?

133
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,480
What do I want?

134
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,240
What do you think?

135
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,040
I'm warning you,

136
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,640
don't try anything funny.

137
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,320
Li Yunhe, what's that supposed to mean?

138
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:36,040
Don't you find me beautiful tonight?

139
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:40,440
Ms. Zhou, you are lovely to behold,

140
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,440
peerless in beauty.

141
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,640
Then why are you acting so coy?

142
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,960
Do you think

143
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,840
I'm not good enough for you?

144
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,280
Li Yunhe,

145
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,760
you had the nerve

146
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,040
to spend our wedding night

147
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,040
in a brothel.

148
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,520
Now I'm asking you to sleep with me,

149
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,120
and you're hemming and hawing?

150
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,440
Are you a man or not?

151
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,240
Ms. Zhou,

152
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,840
I've already signed the divorce papers.

153
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,640
I'm no longer the Zhou son-in-law.

154
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,880
Please behave yourself.

155
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,120
I have things to do.

156
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,320
I'll be going.

157
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,920
Hey, Li Yunhe!

158
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:13,040
Stop right there!

159
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,080
I said stop!

160
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,440
Mr. Li?

161
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,200
Why did he come out

162
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:34,080
of your cousin's room so late?

163
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:36,960
Let's go

164
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,840
see what's happening.

165
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,200
Screw you, Li Yunhe.

166
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,280
I threw myself at you,

167
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,720
and you wouldn't even look me
in the eye?

168
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,720
(Humph, finally came to your senses)

169
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,680
(and came looking for me?)

170
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,720
(Too late.)

171
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,640
(I'm not interested in
talking to you now.)

172
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,480
I'm going to sleep.

173
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,880
My lady, did Mr. Li

174
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,960
do something inappropriate

175
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,440
to Miss Song?

176
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,640
Where's Li Yunhe?

177
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,840
He left.

178
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,600
Huaijin,

179
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,760
why would Li Yunhe come to your room

180
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,760
in the middle of the night?

181
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,280
I called him over.

182
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,240
You...

183
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,160
What's wrong?

184
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,440
Li Yunhe already signed
the divorce letter.

185
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,520
He's no longer
the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

186
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,680
I want to take him
as my live-in husband.

187
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,240
What's wrong with that?

188
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:31,520
Miss Song,
though Mr. Li signed the papers,

189
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,120
my lady hasn't signed them.

190
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,280
He's still the Zhou family's son-in-law.

191
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,960
Exactly. Song Huaijin,

192
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,120
what's gotten into you?

193
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,160
You're quite fickle, aren't you?

194
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,640
You weren't like this before.

195
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,280
Yu,

196
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:45,040
I'm only doing this for your own good.

197
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,640
Even though Li Yunhe helped

198
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,240
restore the silk-making craft,

199
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,600
the Rustling Silk

200
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,640
has already lost
its imperial tribute status.

201
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,840
The Zhou household
is no longer an imperial supplier.

202
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,440
Without that protection,

203
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,720
what will the Zhous

204
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,720
use to fight the Marquis House?

205
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,840
The best course now

206
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,840
is for you
to marry into the Marquis House.

207
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,440
As for me,

208
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,040
I'll take Li Yunhe
as my live-in husband.

209
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,720
Song Huaijin,

210
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,760
you're fighting me over a man?

211
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,520
Fine. I'll take you on right here!

212
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,240
What are you
getting so worked up about, Yu?

213
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,400
I really don't get it.

214
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:14,200
You don't get it? Think about it.

215
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,600
You're a total idiot!

216
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,440
Did your brain

217
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,280
get fried or something?

218
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:19,600
Why are you cursing at me?

219
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,640
Go tell Li Yunhe the truth right now!

220
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,360
Tell him you're the Zhou heiress!

221
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,760
Otherwise, once the Weaving Bureau's
decree arrives

222
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,800
and the Marquis House
moves against the Zhou family,

223
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,280
you'll regret it

224
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:31,240
before you can even blink!

225
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:43,320
Zhao Ziyao, what are you so happy about?

226
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,520
Where were you this morning?

227
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,520
I went to Tang Xian Gambiered Silk
to pick up my order.

228
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,880
The Gambiered Silk I pre-ordered

229
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,040
from Li Yunhe has been delivered.

230
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,000
So this time,

231
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,600
how is the quality of the Gambiered Silk

232
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,360
delivered by the Zhous?

233
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,080
Strange as it is,

234
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:04,400
the quality
of the Zhous' Gambiered Silk this time

235
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,720
is actually better than it was

236
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,160
over a decade ago.

237
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,400
Speaking of a decade ago,

238
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:11,240
I recall something.

239
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,880
Back then, the Weaving Bureau reported

240
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:16,800
that a mysterious fire broke out
at the Feng City's Zhou Manor.

241
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,160
From that point on,

242
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,520
the quality of the Rustling Silk

243
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,400
became inconsistent,
sometimes good, sometimes bad.

244
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,360
I suspect

245
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:26,200
the core crafting technique
for the Zhous' Rustling Silk

246
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,120
was likely lost in that fire,

247
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,840
breaking its generational transmission.

248
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:30,960
What?

249
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,960
The moment
the tribute status was revoked,

250
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,080
the Zhous immediately found

251
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,280
the core technique for Gambiered Silk.

252
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,560
What are they playing at?

253
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,600
Your Highness,

254
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,640
in my humble opinion,

255
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:42,440
the improvement
in the Zhous' Rustling Silk

256
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,000
likely has something to do
with Li Yunhe.

257
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,040
The Zhous would rather risk

258
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,800
offending the Marquis House

259
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,360
than not take Li Yunhe
as their live-in son-in-law.

260
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,160
It seems that brat Li Yunhe

261
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,560
does have some real talent.

262
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,680
Yunzhuo,

263
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,680
how about you send the Shadow Guards

264
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,240
to capture Li Yunhe, castrate him,

265
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,160
and bring him to the palace?

266
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:06,080
So he can weave
Gambiered Silk for me every day?

267
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:09,480
Hmm. Don't even think about it.

268
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,200
(Marquis House)

269
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,200
(Marquis House)
The Zhous have deep roots in Feng City.

270
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,480
They were
even a former imperial supplier.

271
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,800
They have many connections
in official circles.

272
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:18,640
Although

273
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,800
the Rustling Silk has now

274
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,800
been stripped
of its imperial tribute status,

275
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,960
a lion's cub is still a lion.

276
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,600
So we mustn't be hasty.

277
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,240
We must plan slowly and carefully.

278
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,960
Then tell me,

279
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,560
how long must I wait?

280
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,240
Originally, crushing the Zhou household

281
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,320
would have been somewhat difficult.

282
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,080
But blinded by greed,

283
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,600
they listened to Li Yunhe's advice

284
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,480
and launched
that "tribute-grade Rustling Silk"

285
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,160
pre-sale scheme.

286
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:42,160
After it backfired,

287
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:44,840
they even renamed Rustling Silk
to Gambiered Silk.

288
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,440
When it comes time to deliver,

289
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:49,000
if the Zhous can't produce
tribute-grade Gambiered Silk...

290
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:56,360
The Zhous' Gambiered Silk
has been delivered.

291
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,240
My lord,

292
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,560
latest news.

293
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,680
The Zhous' first batch of Gambiered Silk

294
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,760
has been delivered.

295
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,680
What?

296
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:10,860
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)

297
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:17,960
My lord,

298
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,360
what's going on?

299
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,680
See for yourself.

300
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,480
How...

301
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,480
How is this possible?

302
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,400
The finished goods
the Zhous delivered this time

303
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,760
are vastly superior in quality

304
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,600
to what they usually produce.

305
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,360
How did they manage this?

306
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,440
Could it be...

307
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,040
Could it be what?

308
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,600
No, that can't be.

309
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,560
It can't be possible.

310
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:51,760
Li Yunhe is just
a lowly live-in son-in-law.

311
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,480
How could he possibly understand

312
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,080
the crafting process of Rustling Silk?

313
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,640
We'll know soon enough by sending men

314
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:58,120
to the Zhou Manor, dragging him out,

315
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,280
and torturing him.

316
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,720
My lord,

317
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:03,840
the Weaving Bureau's decree
hasn't been delivered yet.

318
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:05,960
The Zhou family
is still the imperial supplier.

319
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,600
Such an action would be inappropriate.

320
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,400
Then what do you suggest?

321
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,400
Well...

322
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,520
My lord, the Zhou family

323
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,800
can get the Prefect
to help them look good.

324
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,280
You're the future Marquis of Zhennan.

325
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,960
Could a mere Feng City Prefect

326
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,800
dare not show you respect?

327
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,560
Alright.

328
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,760
We'll do as you say.

329
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,360
Let's see

330
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,360
if Li Yunhe

331
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,240
can escape my trap

332
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,800
this time.

333
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:50,200
Zhou Xingyu, you,

334
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,200
your family's assets,

335
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,920
and the Gambiered Silk technique

336
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:58,840
are all mine for the taking.

337
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:02,360
(Proclamation)
(Due to days of torrential rain,)

338
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:03,880
(Proclamation)
(severe flooding has occurred.)

339
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:04,960
(Proclamation)
(People are destitute and displaced.)

340
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,440
(Proclamation)
(Flood victims swarmed into Feng City,)

341
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,840
(Proclamation)
(causing grain prices to skyrocket)

342
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,840
(and supplies to run scarce.)

343
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,320
(The Prefect's Office)

344
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,560
(seeks wise and capable individuals)

345
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:13,800
(from across the city)

346
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:14,600
(to offer strategies and counsel)

347
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,120
(to resolve this urgent crisis.)

348
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,520
(The reward is 1,000 taels.)

349
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:20,920
Constable Xing,

350
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,000
Mr. Li is here.

351
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:24,840
May I ask why I was summoned?

352
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,720
You tore down
the official proclamation yourself,

353
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,920
and you ask me what it's about?

354
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,680
Come with us.

355
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,480
The official proclamation?

356
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,400
What official proclamation?

357
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:37,560
You tore it down yourself,

358
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,360
and you ask me?

359
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:41,480
(Feng City Prefectural Office)
(Let's go.)

360
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:43,840
(Feng City Prefectural Office)
(Get in.)

361
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:51,500
(Feng City Prefectural Office)

362
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,640
Then I'll leave it to you, sir.

363
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:56,160
Sir, Li Yunhe is here.

364
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:58,480
Greetings, Prefect.

365
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:06,200
(The Marquis's heir?)

366
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,280
(What's he doing here?)

367
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:14,000
No wonder
the Prefect suddenly summoned me.

368
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,000
So it turns out

369
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:18,000
the Marquis's heir has been missing me.

370
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,960
Don't flatter yourself.

371
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,760
Li Yunhe,

372
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:25,120
didn't you boast
of your overflowing talent

373
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:27,240
and vast learning?

374
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:30,000
I, born of the Marquis House,

375
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,720
naturally have the duty

376
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:35,760
to assist the authorities
and the Feng City Prefect

377
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,400
in recruiting talent.

378
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:38,840
That's right.

379
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:40,760
Li Yunhe,

380
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:43,080
I've heard
you're a man of some capability.

381
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,280
So,

382
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,400
how about you

383
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:48,080
offer some counsel for me here?

384
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,160
Sounds good?

385
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:49,760
Prefect...

386
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:50,280
(Wait a moment.)

387
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:23,780
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

388
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:27,140
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

389
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:30,380
♪Who took the March rain♪

390
00:16:30,620 --> 00:16:33,980
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

391
00:16:34,340 --> 00:16:37,140
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

392
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:40,500
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

393
00:16:41,380 --> 00:16:47,300
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

394
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:50,780
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

395
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:53,860
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

396
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:56,300
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

397
00:16:56,300 --> 00:17:00,500
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

398
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:03,860
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

399
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:07,140
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

400
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:10,580
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

401
00:17:10,740 --> 00:17:17,260
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

402
00:17:43,540 --> 00:17:47,060
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

403
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:50,460
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

404
00:17:51,060 --> 00:17:53,780
♪Who took the March rain♪

405
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:57,300
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

406
00:17:57,700 --> 00:18:00,580
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

407
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:04,380
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

408
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:07,700
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

409
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:10,660
♪As seasons change♪

410
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:14,300
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

411
00:18:14,300 --> 00:18:17,140
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

412
00:18:17,220 --> 00:18:19,780
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

413
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:23,860
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

414
00:18:23,860 --> 00:18:27,180
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

415
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:30,900
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

416
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:34,420
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

417
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:37,300
♪Only for you♪

418
00:18:37,300 --> 00:18:40,900
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

419
00:18:41,020 --> 00:18:43,780
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

420
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:46,460
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

421
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:50,540
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

422
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:53,860
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

423
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:57,260
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

424
00:18:58,100 --> 00:19:03,780
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

425
00:19:04,860 --> 00:19:08,980
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

426
00:19:10,260 --> 00:19:14,780
♪Your wedding gown♪
